      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. i think i might be rounding my back a bit when i pull the bar off the floor. how exactly should i be positioning my spine and torso to make sure it stays neutral? i want to make sure i'm bracing properly.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
